%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-canal%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E/</guid><description>Cannal 完美保持Flannel原生的三种模式，扩展支持Calico的BGP、IPIP模式。并且支持网络策略。 参考链接 Calico网络策略确保CNI</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>Canal</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>k8s基石</category></item><item><title>K8s网络CNI Flannel详细说明</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-31-k8s%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-flannel%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E/</link><pubDate>Thu, 31 Aug 2023 21:19:30 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Thu, 31 Aug 2023 21:19:30 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-31-k8s%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-flannel%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E/</guid><description>Flannel由CoreOS开发，是k8s最成熟的开源CNI插件之一。它提供了一个开箱即用的网络模型，旨在实现更好的容器和主机间的网络。 Fl</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>Flannel</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>k8s基石</category></item><item><title>K8s网络CNI-概念与入门</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-30-k8s%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E4%B8%8E%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/</link><pubDate>Wed, 30 Aug 2023 19:10:41 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Wed, 30 Aug 2023 19:10:41 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-30-k8s%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E4%B8%8E%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/</guid><description>网络架构是 K8S 的一个复杂组件。Kubernetes 网络模型对特定网络功能提出了要求。业界已开发出许多针对特定环境和要求的网络解决方案。 容器网络</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>CNI</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>k8s基石</category></item><item><title>K8s部署实录-6-Flannel版本与5.15内核不兼容导致跨节点pod无法通信问题</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-29-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-6-flannel%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8E5.15%E5%86%85%E6%A0%B8%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%BC%E5%AE%B9%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%B7%A8%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9pod%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Tue, 29 Aug 2023 21:11:32 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Tue, 29 Aug 2023 21:11:32 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-29-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-6-flannel%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8E5.15%E5%86%85%E6%A0%B8%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%BC%E5%AE%B9%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%B7%A8%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9pod%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>Flannel 是 Kubernetes 中常用的 CNI 插件之一，用于为容器提供网络连接。然而，在某些情况下，特定版本的 Flannel 可能与某些内核版本不兼容， 导致 &amp;ldquo;bad udp checksum&amp;rdquo; 错误，从而影响了跨节点</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>Flannel</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>k8s部署实录</category></item><item><title>K8s网络CNI-常见网络插件说明与横向对比</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-30-k8s%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%8E%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94/</link><pubDate>Tue, 29 Aug 2023 21:11:32 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Tue, 29 Aug 2023 21:11:32 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-30-k8s%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%8E%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94/</guid><description>CNI(Container NetworkInterface)意为容器网络接口，它是一种标准的设计，为了让用户在容器创建或销毁时都能够更容易地配置容器网络。 由Goog</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>CNI</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>k8s基石</category></item><item><title>k8s部署实录-5-RKE节点清理指南：确保节点重新部署的顺利进行</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-5-rke%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E6%B8%85%E7%90%86%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</link><pubDate>Tue, 29 Aug 2023 20:05:11 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Tue, 29 Aug 2023 20:05:11 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-5-rke%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E6%B8%85%E7%90%86%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</guid><description>部署集群后出现异常，想重新进行部署，需要在 Kubernetes 集群中清理节点，以确保不影响重新部署。 在本篇博客中，将详细介绍如何使用 RKE（Rancher Kubernetes E</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>RKE</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>k8s部署实录</category></item><item><title>k8s部署实录-3-rke部署集群忽略docker版本校验</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-3-rke%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E5%BF%BD%E7%95%A5docker%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C/</link><pubDate>Mon, 28 Aug 2023 21:15:10 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Mon, 28 Aug 2023 21:15:10 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-3-rke%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E5%BF%BD%E7%95%A5docker%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C/</guid><description>重要 前因： 由于客户现场不给root权限，docker-ce为客户自行安装，版本为24.0.5, 与准备的安装包不兼容（rke版本为v1.2.6</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>RKE</category><category>k8s部署实录</category></item><item><title>k8s部署实录-2-rke指定ssh_key_path配置从而替换默认路径</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-2-rke%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9Assh_key_path%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%BB%8E%E8%80%8C%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84/</link><pubDate>Mon, 28 Aug 2023 20:28:18 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Mon, 28 Aug 2023 20:28:18 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-2-rke%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9Assh_key_path%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%BB%8E%E8%80%8C%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2%E9